oundary/handoff concern. I rejected System because the behavior text does not require subprocess/network fault behavior; it requires correct internal sequencing with DB state checks.","test_description":"Start with an empty test database, run the runner with at least one migration, and assert _migrations exists before first migration record insertion and that migration application succeeds only after metadata table creation.","plan_consistent":true,"plan_consistent_note":null,"level_probabilities":{"Unit":0.05,"Integration":0.7,"System":0.25,"Agentic":0,"Workflow":0}}]}
